==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪkɪt|-ɪkɪt]]

===Adjective===

'''cricket'''

#''(mainly UK)'' Describing an act that is very fair and sportsmanlike, derived from the sport.
#:''That player's foul wasn't '''cricket'''!''

===Noun===
{{wikipedia|Cricket (insect)}}
{{en-noun}}

#An insect in the order [[Orthoptera]] that makes a [[chirping]] sound by rubbing its [[wing]] [[casing]]s against [[comb]]s on its [[hind leg]]s.

